Description of the table C_PIB_DEVICE_UPGRADE

20-Nov-2022

 

Tracks Upgrades of Software version upgrades captured in MP1 via the measurement tables. As of version 20-Nov-2022 is Software, SMA upgrades only.

 

Source: IMPTT.MPTYP = 'S'

IMPTT.POINT = IMRG.POINT

 

Update Frequency: Daily Creates or Updates
